      "en": "Belgian endive is a 19th-century Belgian invention. By forcing chicory roots in the dark, the white, mildly bitter head develops. Belgium is the birthplace of this vegetable and produces hundreds of tonnes annually.",
      "fr": "L'endive est une invention belge du XIXe si\u00e8cle. En for\u00e7ant les racines de chicor\u00e9e dans l'obscurit\u00e9, on obtient le chicon blanc, l\u00e9g\u00e8rement amer. La Belgique est le berceau de ce l\u00e9gume."
