      "en": "Fully submerged aquatic plant with crimped, wavy-edged leaves 3\u20138 cm long. The leaves have a characteristic 'corrugated iron' structure at the margins. Flowers with tiny pink spikes above the water surface. Overwinters as turions (specialised overwintering buds).",
      "fr": "Plante aquatique enti\u00e8rement submerg\u00e9e aux feuilles crisp\u00e9es et ondul\u00e9es de 3\u20138 cm de long. Les feuilles ont une structure caract\u00e9ristique en 't\u00f4le ondul\u00e9e' aux marges. Fleurit avec de minuscules \u00e9pis roses au-dessus de la surface de l'eau."
