      "en": "Photosynthesis; grows on moderately nutrient-poor, calcareous to neutral soils in open, sunny situations. Benefits from extensive management.",
      "fr": "Photosynth\u00e8se; pousse sur sols mod\u00e9r\u00e9ment pauvres, calcaires \u00e0 neutres, en situations ouvertes et ensoleill\u00e9es."
