      "en": "Low-growing annual with small white flowers where the five deeply notched petals appear to be ten. The stem has a characteristic single line of hairs on one side. Edible and nutritious; popular with birds and small mammals.",
      "fr": "Plante annuelle basse aux petites fleurs blanches o\u00f9 les cinq p\u00e9tales profond\u00e9ment \u00e9chancr\u00e9s semblent en \u00eatre dix. La tige a une caract\u00e9ristique ligne de poils d'un c\u00f4t\u00e9. Comestible et nutritive; appr\u00e9ci\u00e9e des oiseaux et petits mammif\u00e8res."
