      "en": "Small, evergreen dwarf shrub with leathery, glossy leaves that have black dots on the underside. The white to pale pink bell-shaped flowers bloom in May-June. The red, shiny berries are tart but edible and rich in vitamin C.",
      "fr": "Petit arbuste nain \u00e0 feuilles persistantes, coriaces et brillantes portant des points noirs en dessous. Les fleurs en cloche blanches \u00e0 rose p\u00e2le fleurissent en mai-juin. Les baies rouges et brillantes sont \u00e2pres mais comestibles et riches en vitamine C."
