      "en": "Dry, calcareous grasslands, roadsides, woodland edges and rock faces; common in the Ardennes and Meuse area, rarer in Flanders.",
      "fr": "Prairies calcaires s\u00e8ches, bords de routes, lisi\u00e8res foresti\u00e8res et falaises; commun en Ardenne et dans la r\u00e9gion mosane, plus rare en Flandre."
