      "en": "Salt marshes, coastal rocks, saline road verges and coastal beaches; rarer at inland saline sites.",
      "fr": "Pr\u00e9s sal\u00e9s, rochers c\u00f4tiers, bords de routes salins et plages c\u00f4ti\u00e8res; plus rare en sites salins int\u00e9rieurs."
