      "en": "Elegant woodland plant with arching stems bearing alternate oval leaves and drooping greenish-white bell-shaped flowers in clusters of 2\u20135. Flowers May\u2013June. Black berries are poisonous. The knobbly rhizome left seal-like scars when harvested in former times.",
