      "en": "Graceful perennial with narrow grass-like leaves and branched flower stems to 80 cm bearing white six-petalled star-shaped flowers. Flowers June\u2013August. Distinguished from the unbranched St Bernard's lily (A. liliago) by the strongly branched stem. Protected in Belgium.",
      "fr": "Gracieuse vivace aux feuilles \u00e9troites gazonnantes et tiges florales ramifi\u00e9es jusqu'\u00e0 80 cm portant des fleurs \u00e9toil\u00e9es blanches \u00e0 six p\u00e9tales. Floraison juin\u2013ao\u00fbt. Se distingue du non-ramifi\u00e9 (A. liliago) par sa tige tr\u00e8s ramifi\u00e9e. Prot\u00e9g\u00e9 en Belgique."
