      "en": "Impressive fast-growing tree to 35 m with grey-white smooth bark and strongly two-coloured leaves: dark green above, white-woolly beneath. Leaves shimmer in wind. Flowers early spring with drooping catkins before leaves. Readily produces root suckers.",
