      "en": "Slow-growing evergreen shrub or small tree to 8 m with small glossy oval leaves. Well-known garden ornamental for borders, hedges and topiary. Flowers early in spring with small yellowish blooms. Attacked by box moth (Cydalima perspectalis). Mildly poisonous.",
      "fr": "Arbuste ou petit arbre sempervirent \u00e0 croissance lente jusqu'\u00e0 8 m aux petites feuilles ovales brillantes. Ornement de jardin pour bordures, haies et topiaires. Fleurit t\u00f4t au printemps. Attaqu\u00e9 par la pyrale du buis (Cydalima perspectalis). L\u00e9g\u00e8rement toxique."
