      "en": "Imposing waterside plant with erect sword-shaped leaves to 1.5 m and large yellow flowers with brown-veined falls. Flowers May\u2013July. Poisonous if ingested (irisin). Symbol of the Belgian Flemish lion and classic heraldic motif. Seed pod large and three-chambered.",
