      "en": "Biennial or short-lived perennial 30\u2013100 cm. White flowers open in evening and scented, May\u2013September. Dioecious. Inflated calyx. Closely related to red campion (Silene dioica) and crosses with it. Scented flowers pollinated by moths. Can hybridize with red campion.",
