      "en": "Perennial 60\u2013150 cm with large yellow flower heads July\u2013September. Hollow stems with white latex. Leaves with soft spines. Perennial roots going deep in soil; difficult to control on arable land. Fruits with white fluffy pappus for wind dispersal.",
