      "en": "Graceful, straggling perennial 20\u201360 cm with narrow, grass-like leaves. White flowers with deeply notched petals May\u2013August. Resembles chickweed but larger and with narrower leaves. Grows in dense mats. Characteristic of acidic, nutrient-poor grasslands.",
