      "en": "Annual to biennial herb 10\u201350 cm. Reddish, strongly aromatic stems. Leaves pinnate, deeply cut. Small pink-red flowers with 5 petals (April\u2013October). Seed catapult mechanism for dispersal. Strongly scented when crushed.",
