      "en": "Annual to perennial herb with prostrate or ascending stems. Small yellow flowers in globose clusters (April\u2013October). Leaves trifoliate like clover. Fruits small black coiled pods (hence 'lupulina'). Nitrogen-fixer via symbiosis with Rhizobium bacteria.",
